119
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:26,720
No need.

120
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:28,640
I can't stay long.

121
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,040
But rest assured.

122
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,920
Regarding the underreporting taxes,

123
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:41,000
I will report everything to His Majesty.

124
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:43,720
Wait for the decree.

125
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,760
Mr. Wen!

126
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:47,760
Please, let's talk this out properly.

127
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:50,320
How much do you want?

128
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:51,760
I won't bargain.

129
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:54,600
You better

130
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,160
stop talking,

131
00:07:58,120 --> 00:08:00,040
for I will repeat everything

132
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:02,040
