133
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,800
Mr. Wen!

134
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,720
Wen Su,

135
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:17,400
I won't let you off easily.

136
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:21,240
So who is the boss, Mr. Luo or Ms. Chen?

137
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,560
They're a couple.

138
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:23,640
They are both bosses.

139
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:24,960
Wait,

140
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:27,840
I remember Mr. Luo
only came to Qingzhou later.

141
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:29,360
And the two never got married.

142
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:39,880
Baoyin,

143
00:08:40,800 --> 00:08:42,800
some official's here
to bring down Prefect Feng.

144
00:08:42,800 --> 00:08:44,240
Now Feng wants a refund.

145
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:48,320
This old miser
should have been punished long ago.

146
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:50,520
He won't be around for long.

147
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,320
It's better to avoid trouble.

148
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,560
Just give him what he wants.

149
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:54,600
But the thing is

150
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,880
that man from the capital ate
a bowl of seafood wontons.

151
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,360
There's no way to return it.

152
00:08:58,920 --> 00:09:00,240
Seafood wontons?

153
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:04,240
People from the capital also love these?

154
00:09:10,163 --> 00:09:12,928
(Capital Street)

155
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:16,520
Mr. Wen.

156
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:17,480
Mr. Wen is coming.

157
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:19,200
(Song Shulan)
Quickly now.

158
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,000
Tidy up.

159
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,400
Or Mr. Wen will report us.

160
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,920
That book is a private copy.
Hide it quickly.

161
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:24,960
Okay, okay.

162
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:32,000
So this is the God of Justice
of Ministry of Revenue,

163
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,520
Wen Su.

164
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:35,000
Please come again.

165
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:39,000
Take a look.

166
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:51,080
Ms. Song.

167
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:52,640
Apologies.

168
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,480
You know me?

169
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,680
In the entire capital,

170
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,800
you are the only woman

171
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,760
who loves to buy the stationery

172
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:03,440
and uses a man's folding fan.

173
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,600
And yet you rejected me three times.

174
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,840
I have my pride, you know.

175
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,240
I always wanted to see

176
00:10:08,640 --> 00:10:10,400
what kind of man

177
00:10:10,400 --> 00:10:11,560
the famous God of Justice is.

178
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:12,960
Now I see

179
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,320
you are just an average man.

180
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:15,960
We can just drop

181
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,280
my rejection.

182
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,760
I am the daughter of Minister Song.

183
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:20,760
Am I not worthy?

184
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:22,200
Why would you humiliate me?

185
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,640
Mr. Wen!

186
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:26,840
They're here.

187
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:31,680
If you'll excuse me.

188
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,200
I already said it.

189
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:52,840
The wine can't enter.

190
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,120
Either drink it

191
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:54,760
or throw it.

192
00:10:55,640 --> 00:10:56,120
Sir.

193
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:57,680
The wine is home-brewed.

194
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,000
Winter is here

195
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,960
and we are visiting relatives.

196
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:02,120
Please let us in.

197
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,560
Daqing Laws

198
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:05,040
prohibit the private sale of yeast.

199
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,840
Who knows if you are

200
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,920
gifting or selling it.

201
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:10,360
Luo.

202
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:27,600
Sir.

203
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,000
You've worked hard

204
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,080
in this weather.

205
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:31,760
Take this.

206
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:33,320
Buy some food for your men.

207
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:34,680
Take it back.

208
00:11:34,880 --> 00:11:35,720
Rules are rules.

209
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:38,200
Let me tell you,

210
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,720
the Ministry of Revenue...

211
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:41,440
Mr. Wen is here.

212
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:52,000
(It's him.)

213
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:05,440
It's fine.

214
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,480
